  <Document>
    <name>Japan Dining Map - Osaka</name>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Alarde</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Alarde</strong><br/>Osaka / Osaka<br/>Address: 1F, 1-14-4, Awaza, Nishi-ku, Osaka-shi, Osaka<br/>Nearest: 3-minute walk from Honmachi Station Exit 23 (Osaka Municipal Subway Line)<br/>Cuisine: Other Western cuisine<br/>Reservation: Reservation request<br/>Dinner range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Dinner: JPY 16,500 - 16,500<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 16,500 - 16,500<br/>Summary: Alarde is a friendly, 1-star, world gourmet guide awarded restaurant that serves Basque cuisine made using a Spanish-style stone kiln oven in the relaxed Honmachi business district of Osaka.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244373/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.494021,34.680827,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Kashiwaya Osaka Kitashinchi</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Kashiwaya Osaka Kitashinchi</strong><br/>Osaka / Osaka<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Reservation request<br/>Dinner range: $$$$$ JPY 30k+<br/>Dinner: JPY 34,650 - 34,650<br/>Child policy: Children are welcome those who can eat the same menu as adults (16 years old and older) are welcome<br/>Summary: A new branch of Kashiwaya Osaka Senriyama, a 3-star restaurant, located in Kitashinchi, Osaka, that offers Japanese cuisine inspired by the four seasons.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/245441/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Approximate location based on public geocoding unless replaced by stronger source matching.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.5014539,34.6937569,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Kitashinichi Tempura Bonji</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Kitashinichi Tempura Bonji</strong><br/>Osaka / Osaka<br/>Address: 3F, 1-3-16, Dojima, Kita-ku, Osaka-shi, Osaka<br/>Nearest: A 1-minute walk from &quot;Nishi-Umeda Station&quot;, Exit C-92 (Osaka City Subway Yotsubashi Line); A 3-minute walk from &quot;Kita-Shinchi Station&quot;, Exit 11 (JR Tozai Line )<br/>Cuisine: Tempura<br/>Reservation: Reservation request<br/>Dinner range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Dinner: JPY 10,000 - 12,800<br/>Child policy: Children of elementary school age and older are welcome as long as they eat the same course meal as adults<br/>Summary: An open counter tempura restaurant famous for breaking from tradition and serving unimaginable varieties and combinations of tempura that will both surprise and delight its guests.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244793/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.497225,34.696607,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>LIAISON</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>LIAISON</strong><br/>Osaka / Osaka<br/>Cuisine: French<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Dinner: JPY 18,150 - 22,385<br/>Lunch range: $$ JPY 5k-10k<br/>Lunch: JPY 9,680 - 13,915<br/>Child policy: Junior high school students and above are welcome<br/>Summary: A 1-star restaurant in Osaka, named in celebration of its traditional French cuisine being created in harmony with Japanese terroir, ingredients and produce.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/245288/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Approximate location based on public geocoding unless replaced by stronger source matching.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.5014539,34.6937569,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Sushi Ichiei</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Sushi Ichiei</strong><br/>Osaka / Osaka<br/>Address: B1F Senju Bldg., 1-6-10, Sennichimae, Chuo-ku, Osaka-shi, Osaka<br/>Nearest: 5 minutes on foot from Exit 2 of Nihonbashi Station on the Osaka Municipal Subway Sennichimae Line and Tetsudou Sakaisuji Line<br/>Cuisine: Sushi<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 22,000 - 22,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$$ JPY 20k+<br/>Lunch: JPY 22,000 - 22,000<br/>Child policy: Junior high school students and above are welcome<br/>Summary: A sushi restaurant in Sennichimae, Osaka, that offers extraordinary nigiri sushi crafted by a chef who inherited his sushi-making DNA from his father and learned the sophisticated art of sushi at renowned sushi restaurants.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/245457/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.5045345,34.668091,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Sushi Yuden</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Sushi Yuden</strong><br/>Osaka / Osaka<br/>Address: 3-8-25, Uesio, Tennoji-ku, Osaka-shi, Osaka<br/>Nearest: A 1-minute walk from Tanimachi 9-chome of Osaka Municipal Subway Tanimachi Line; A 3-minute walk from  Osaka Uehommachi of Kintetsu Namba Line<br/>Cuisine: Sushi<br/>Reservation: Reservation request<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 27,830 - 27,830<br/>Lunch range: $$$$ JPY 20k+<br/>Lunch: JPY 27,830 - 27,830<br/>Child policy: Children are welcome but must be able to eat the same course as an adult<br/>Summary: A 1-star sushi restaurant tucked away in Osaka with warm hospitality and a fiercely loyal clientele.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/245112/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.51678724586964,34.66625908756479,0</coordinates>
