    <Placemark>
      <name>Sushidokoro Kurosugi</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Sushidokoro Kurosugi</strong><br/>Osaka / Osaka<br/>Address: 2F, Shindai Building, 1-2-1, Dojimahama, Kita-ku, Osaka-shi, Osaka<br/>Nearest: A 7-minute walk from Kitashinchi Station(JR Tozai Line)<br/>Cuisine: Sushi<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 24,200 - 24,200<br/>Lunch range: $$$$ JPY 20k+<br/>Lunch: JPY 22,000 - 22,000<br/>Child policy: Elementary school students and above are welcome<br/>Summary: A world gourmet guide awarded restaurant, serving the latest in Osaka-style &quot;Edomae&quot; sushi.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244608/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>135.4993012547493,34.69568547012702,0</coordinates>
