    <Placemark>
      <name>Tempura Kawaharasaki</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Tempura Kawaharasaki</strong><br/>Osaka / Osaka<br/>Address: 1F, 3-1-5, Nishitemma, Kita-ku, Osaka-shi, Osaka<br/>Nearest: A 5-minute walk from Kitahama Station, Exit 26（Keihan Main Line） <br/>Cuisine: Tempura<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Dinner: JPY 16,170 - 23,100<br/>Child policy: Junior high school students and above are welcome<br/>Summary: Experience light &quot;Kamigata Tempura&quot; that represents Osaka, using high quality Setouchi fish.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244756/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
