    <Placemark>
      <name>Yugen</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Yugen</strong><br/>Osaka / Osaka<br/>Address: 1F, Zeniya Honpo, 14-14, Uehommachi, Tennoji-ku, Osaka-shi, Osaka<br/>Nearest: A 5-minutes walk from Osaka Uehommachi Station on the Kintetsu Osaka Line<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 20,790 - 28,875<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 11,550 - 11,550<br/>Summary: A 2-star Japanese restaurant run by a former chef of Ajikitcho, offering kaiseki dishes that showcase locally grown vegetables and produce from all over Japan.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/245106/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
